Like you've never done it.

Erin and I have agreed to each post an image a day on LJ. Why, you ask? Why the fuck not? We're both photographers and this is an exercise in discipline. Feel free to comment. Any offers of sex, drugs, and/or cash will be considered.


This image was taken in downtown Sacramento, near the Capitol building.
